library(tidyr)
fixname <- function(x){ #
    names(x)<-enc2native(names(x)) #
    return(x)
}
ks_temp <- 
  ks %>%
  filter(=="2014"|=="2015") %>%
  select(, , , , , ) %>% #
  pivot_wider(names_from = , values_from = , names_sep="") %>%#
  rename(2014="2014", 2015="2015") %>% #
  fixname()

p4_0 <- ggplot(data=ks_temp, mapping=aes(x=2014, y=2015))
(p4_1 <- p4_0 + geom_point())

(p4_2 <- p4_1 + facet_wrap(~)) #

(p4_3 <- p4_1 + facet_grid(~)) #

print(ks_temp1415, n=50)
